wiki.content:
Blues at it's finest from the Ice Man, Albert Collins.  He was a clear influence on Stevie Ray Vaughn with the loose and aggressive but ever articulate Telecaster riffs.  This song is guaranteed to kick things up a notch and great to sing along with when you ain't drunk but just drinkin...
